They betrayed me.<br />
They left me starved out of my house and home after I taught them for nearly half a year.<br />
Stopped paying. Same excuse as you. Said they couldn't afford it anymore.<br />
Thought they could just get up and leave me without paying their dues for what I taught them.<br />
Thought they could do it on their own or teach other people <strong>my</strong> knowledge.<br />
Thought they could make it in the world by cheating me out of <strong>my</strong> knowledge.<br />
But the truth is, none of you fucking vermin can.<br />
You're nothing in this world without <strong>me</strong> and <strong>my</strong> knowledge.<br />
